69.notes:
For Property sites like http://dubai.grand.hyatt.com/en/hotel/home.html
The site_id variable is not getting set correctly in the UDO on the booking flow pages (rooms and rates, guest info, confirmation). It should contain the global hyatt report suite AND the property id eg. "hyhyattcom,hydxbgh"

However, the "dxbgh" (spirit code) portion of the report suite is avaiable in the variable "product_id" of the UDO. So, we use this variable to append the expected report suite (with a "hy" prefix") to the report suite.
